div.p: Several crystals of FetA-ePchFe obtained in new crystallization conditions were tested. All of them diffracted X-ray at very low resolution. Very thin crystals obtained in a previous crystallization condition diffracted X-ray beyond 4 A resolution and data were collected at 3 A resolution.
